text: The 1901 Washington & Jefferson Presidents football team was an American football team that represented Washington & Jefferson College as an independent during the 1911 college football season. In its second season under head coach William B. Seaman, the team compiled a 6–2–2 record and outscored opponents by a total of 125 to 39. ==Schedule== ==References== Washington Category:Washington & Jefferson Presidents football seasons Washington and Jefferson football
